<https://example.com/id/NotesOnElizabethSimcoeSketches> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#history> "Custodial History: The material in this sub-series was acquired in 1952 under the terms of a long-term loan agreement with the University of Toronto Library, which owns the records." .
<https://example.com/id/NotesOnElizabethSimcoeSketches> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#isDirectlyIncludedIn> <https://example.com/id/ElizabethSimcoeSketches> .
